code: public void testAbdicateAfterVotingConfigExclusionAdded() throws ExecutionException, InterruptedException {     internalCluster().startNodes(2).     final String originalMaster = internalCluster().getMasterName().     logger.info("--> excluding master node {}", originalMaster).     client().execute(AddVotingConfigExclusionsAction.INSTANCE, new AddVotingConfigExclusionsRequest(new String[] { originalMaster })).get().     client().admin().cluster().prepareHealth().setWaitForEvents(Priority.LANGUID).get().     assertNotEquals(originalMaster, internalCluster().getMasterName()). }
